library.name: con-subd
library.description:
SUB-D Connectors

Harting
NorComp

PREFIX :
H = High density
F = Female
M = Male

NUMBER: Number of pins

SUFFIX :
H = Horizontal
V = Vertical
P = Shield pin on housing
B = No mounting holes
S = Pins individually placeable (Single)
D = Direct mounting

Created by librarian@cadsoft.de
